1. Find all dead cells that are neighbors of at least one live cell (candidate cells)
2. Check which of those dead cells have exactly 3 live neighbors
3. Add those newly born cells to the surviving cells

Write the minimal code to make all 7 tests pass. Run `pnpm test` to verify.

